classDiagram
    class Owner {
        -String name
        -String phoneNumber
        -int availability
        -Map preferences
        -List~Pet~ pets
        +addPet(pet) void
        +editPet(pet) void
        +removePet(pet) void
        +viewPets() List~Pet~
        +viewAllTasks() List~Task~
    }

    class Pet {
        -String name
        -String species
        -int age
        -List~String~ medicalConditions
        -List~Task~ tasks
        +addTask(task) void
        +editTask(task) void
        +removeTask(task) void
        +completeTask(task) Task
        +viewTasks() List~Task~
    }

    class Task {
        -String name
        -int duration
        -String time
        -int priority
        -String category
        -boolean isComplete
        -String recurrence
        -Date dueDate
        +updateDetails(details) void
        +markComplete() void
        +nextOccurrence() Task
    }

    class Scheduler {
        -List~Task~ tasks
        -int availability
        -Map preferences
        -Map petByTask
        -List~Task~ plan
        -String explanation
        +generatePlan() List~Task~
        +organizeByPriority(tasks) List~Task~
        +sortByTime(tasks) List~Task~
        +filterByPet(tasks, petName) List~Task~
        +detectConflicts(tasks) List~String~
        +filterToConstraints(tasks) List~Task~
        +explainPlan() String
    }

    Owner "1" *-- "0..*" Pet : owns
    Pet "1" *-- "0..*" Task : has
    Scheduler "1" o-- "0..*" Task : schedules
    Pet ..> Task : creates via completeTask
    Task ..> Task : creates next occurrence

    note for Scheduler "Links tasks back to pets via petByTask map (id(task) -> pet name), not a direct reference."
